      "question": "The system $3x - 5y = 2$ and $6x - 10y = k$ has infinitely many solutions. What is the value of $k$?",
      "answer": "(A)",
      "solution": {
        "steps": [
          "For infinitely many solutions, $a_1/a_2 = b_1/b_2 = c_1/c_2$.",
